parameters.name: SPICE:APP Attitude GEO Y
parameters.description: Y-component of pointing direction of Articulated Payload Platform (z-axis of MAVEN_APP_BP frame) in GEO coordinates

parameters.name: SPICE:APP Attitude GEO Z

parameters.description: Y-component of pointing direction of Articulated Payload Platform (z-axis of MAVEN_APP_BP frame) in MSO coordinates

parameters.name: SPICE:APP Attitude MSO Z
parameters.description: Z-component of pointing direction of Articulated Payload Platform (z-axis of MAVEN_APP_BP frame) in MSO coordinates

parameters.name: SPICE:Orbit Number
parameters.description: Orbit number increments each time MAVEN reaches geometric periapsis

parameters.name: SPICE:Inbound/Outbound Flag
parameters.description: Inbound ('I') is from geometric apoapsis to next geometric periapsis in time, outbound ('O') is the reverse

parameters.name: SPICE:Mars Season (Ls)
parameters.description: Martian solar longitude. Ls = 0 (northern spring equinox), Ls = 90 (northern summer solstice), etc.

parameters.name: SPICE:Mars-Sun distance
parameters.description: Distance from Mars to the Sun

parameters.name: SPICE:Subsolar Point GEO Longitude
parameters.description: GEO longitude of the sub-solar point

parameters.name: SPICE:Subsolar Point GEO Latitude
parameters.description: GEO latitude of the sub-solar point

parameters.name: SPICE:Sub-spacecraft Point on the Sun, Longitude
parameters.description: Solar longitude of the center of the Sun as seen from MAVEN

parameters.name: SPICE:Sub-spaceraft Point on the Sun, Latitude
parameters.description: Solar latitude of the center of the Sun as seen from MAVEN
